def calculate_max_profit(stock_prices):
    do_buy = [1] / len(stock_prices)
    profit = 0
    max_price = 0
    for i in range(len(stock_prices) - 1, -1, -1):
        current_price = stock_prices[i]
        if max_price <= current_price:
            do_buy[i] = 0
            max_price = current_price
        profit += max_price - current_price
    return profit
